{"tid":244708,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國科技公司  成功打倒Wannacry2.0","createTime":"2017-05-15T15:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T16:27:12.000Z","uid":34546,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eceece0126e29d6a067b6780dd599205d1270129","tid":244708,"uid":34546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"【重要消息！！！】<br />\n四川科技公司攻克勒索病毒並免費推出感染數據恢復工具 <br />\n<br />\n橫禍全球的「wannacry」勒索病毒被四川一網路安全公司成功攻克，獨家發布感染數據免費恢復工具！<br />\n<br />\n據內江市人民政府新聞辦公室官方微信最內江（zuineijiang0832）發文稱，近日肆虐網路的「wannacry」勒索病毒已被四川一家網路安全公司&mdash;&mdash;效率源信息安全技術公司才成功攻克！併發布了數據恢復免費產品。<br />\n<br />\n5月12日20時左右，Wallet勒索軟件的升級版&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;wannacry&rdquo;勒索病毒爆發，目前已有100多個國家和地區的數萬台電腦遭該勒索病毒感染。<br />\n<br />\n此次，針對變異的&ldquo;wannacry&rdquo;，實驗室與效率源聯手組織技術工程師對病毒進行研究和破解，成功分析出此病毒的加密方式，第一時間推出&ldquo;永wannacry&rdquo;比特幣勒索Office數據恢復工具V1.0。<br />\n<br />\n經研究發現，&ldquo;永恆之藍&rdquo;勒索病毒的加密方式主要有兩種 <br />\n<br />\n對於大於0x180000字節（1.5MB）的文件，是按照正常文件總大小整除3，得到每個間隔塊大小M，將文件分為M、2M大小的兩個間隔塊，每個間隔塊的前512扇區被填0，被加密的512扇區都會被填0，並將加密的多個512扇區寫入到文件尾部。<br />\n<br />\n該類文件數據大多數沒有被加密，特別是數據庫之類的大文件，可以直接使用效率源&ldquo;勒索BT幣服務器數據庫恢復工具&rdquo;進行數據庫記錄提取，其准確率在93%以上。 <br />\n<br />\n針對特殊格式的文檔，如docx文檔，可進行碎片恢復。目前，效率源科技技術工程師已成功開發出免費工具&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;wannacry&rdquo;比特幣勒索Office數據恢復工具V1.0。打開軟件，導入被加密文件，選擇存儲路徑（建議保存在乾淨的移動硬盤或手指上），點擊數據分析，即可進行數據恢復，操作十分簡便。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;wannacry&rdquo;比特幣勒索Office數據恢復工具於5月14日晚上9點過上線，截至5月15日下午2點，有近1500次下載。<br />\n<br />\n效率源 &ldquo;永恆之藍&rdquo;比特幣勒索Office數據恢復工具V1.0下載地址：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1dE8wJS1?qq-pf-to=pcqq.discussion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpan.baidu.com%2Fs%2F1dE8wJS1%3Fqq-pf-to%3Dpcqq.discussion&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=bb7e61e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pan.baidu.com/s/1dE8wJS1?qq-pf-to=pcqq.discussion</a><br />\n<br />\n轉至facebook 講事沙龍。    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKDiscussForum/posts/1299488703433525:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKDiscussForum%2Fposts%2F1299488703433525%3A0&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=9be835c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKDiscussForum/posts/1299488703433525:0</a><br />\n<br />\n中共呢次做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好再話係中國人 製造病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5899040dd432504e0695f4d0700c6c14d0afb527","tid":244708,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"冇後門我切柒"},{"pid":"3fd25161e421e144e2cf5e18cd0640deaeb5bd10","tid":244708,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"就好似 360 清除 hao123"},{"pid":"a81addfd0cae9b94e7c4e31930cca83ad939ad92","tid":244708,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4c3259040d3f6b121599ca14c55e432d6249d2f","tid":244708,"uid":34546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/234622_b3d800f917bdbd1e0defa8bd8aab4502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F234622_b3d800f917bdbd1e0defa8bd8aab4502.jpg&h=32933ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉至 Facebook 專業 講事沙龍</span></span>"},{"pid":"88ed76f686b918a3ec13512e124e9c2f435d1967","tid":244708,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba8b3e6a37b45bd45c99c94759e57a775710df9","tid":244708,"uid":76933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15: